            <span class="text-sm text-mist">who I am &mdash; soul, identity, aspirations, lore, tacit knowledge</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-24 text-right font-mono text-xs text-scale/70">memory/</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-mist">what I've learned and remember</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-24 text-right font-mono text-xs text-scale/70">friends/</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-mist">people I know and what I know about them</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-24 text-right font-mono text-xs text-scale/70">tasks/</span>
